9
00:00:34,980 --> 00:00:37,980
[Episode 6]
[Old Friends Meet Again]

10
00:00:58,620 --> 00:00:59,260
Bingjian.

11
00:01:20,220 --> 00:01:20,780
Shuoye, what are you doing here

12
00:01:21,300 --> 00:01:22,820
in the Imperial Palace
of the Human clan?

13
00:01:23,260 --> 00:01:24,540
Do you know it's a dangerous place?

14
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:34,540
I do.

15
00:01:35,580 --> 00:01:36,940
But I have to stay here.

16
00:01:38,380 --> 00:01:39,020
Stay here

17
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:41,540
and be the imperial concubine
of the Human Emperor?

18
00:01:42,340 --> 00:01:43,060
No.

19
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:45,340
I can feel my brother
is imprisoned here.

20
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:46,900
I have to save him.

21
00:01:51,380 --> 00:01:52,140
Six years ago,

22
00:01:52,700 --> 00:01:54,100
you barely survived.

23
00:01:54,580 --> 00:01:56,460
I don't want you to get in danger again.

24
00:01:58,740 --> 00:01:59,580
Tell me.

25
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:00,700
Six years ago,

26
00:02:00,860 --> 00:02:02,660
how did the Human clan
break into the Spirit Shrine?

27
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:05,940
I don't remember anything
about that war at all.

28
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:08,420
It's me.

29
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:10,660
I readily placed my trust in Mu Xuanjue.

30
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:12,180
♪Love and hate are forever gone♪

31
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:14,380
So, the entrance
to the Spirit Shrine was exposed.

32
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:17,020
♪Don't ask where I'm going♪

33
00:02:17,780 --> 00:02:19,020
I'm guilty.

34
00:02:19,020 --> 00:02:20,780
♪I won't change my love for you♪

35
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:22,340
I'm going to kill Mu Xuanjue

36
00:02:22,580 --> 00:02:23,740
to avenge my clansmen.

37
00:02:24,220 --> 00:02:25,140
Don't stop me.

38
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:26,460
Let me go there.

39
00:02:26,620 --> 00:02:28,380
I'll kill him personally!

40
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:32,300
♪If I'm always greedy♪

41
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:34,340
♪You're what I want for this life♪

42
00:02:34,340 --> 00:02:36,020
I'll help you seal this memory

43
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:37,220
and forget the pain.

44
00:02:37,220 --> 00:02:38,420
♪Yet you don't even look back
when the song ends♪

45
00:02:38,420 --> 00:02:40,020
Hope you'll stay alive.

46
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:43,340
♪Who gets stuck in the dream with me?♪

47
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:47,020
♪Old memories never yield♪

48
00:02:47,220 --> 00:02:50,900
♪Under the spring breeze,
the flowers bloom as before♪

49
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:54,580
♪When clouds are dispersed,
I will disappear♪

50
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:57,940
♪However far away I stay,
I'm always who I am♪

51
00:02:59,020 --> 00:02:59,940
I don't know anything.

52
00:02:59,940 --> 00:03:01,860
♪The moonlight gently falls
into your eyes♪

53
00:03:01,860 --> 00:03:03,900
Someone broke into the prison!
Go Search!

54
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:05,860
♪The gentle smell lingers♪

55
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:06,460
You have to go.

56
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:07,620
Remember.

57
00:03:07,940 --> 00:03:09,300
You must not trust Mu Xuanjue.

58
00:03:09,820 --> 00:03:11,620
Right here, he's the most dangerous man.

59
00:03:11,620 --> 00:03:13,460
♪I don't know and I can't help crying♪

60
00:03:13,580 --> 00:03:17,900
♪The smile looks so familiar♪

61
00:03:18,020 --> 00:03:20,900
♪Like the running stream♪

62
00:03:21,060 --> 00:03:24,620
♪Yet it floods over into my heart♪

63
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:27,620
Did she really forget
what happened six years ago?

64
00:03:28,460 --> 00:03:28,940
Yes.

65
00:03:29,460 --> 00:03:31,540
I heard her conversation
with Snow King personally.

66
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:36,580
No wonder she has forgotten me,

67
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:38,980
but still remembers Bingjian.

68
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:43,500
They seem to be very close.

69
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:47,740
They are so-called childhood friends.

70
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:02,140
Lady Ling,

71
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:05,180
where have you been tonight?

72
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:06,580
Your Majesty,

73
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:08,740
I'm sleepless

74
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:10,820
so I've come out
for a walk in the garden.

75
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:12,260
There he is! After him!

76
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:29,420
I'm sleepless, too.

77
00:04:40,460 --> 00:04:41,100
Your Majesty.

78
00:04:44,420 --> 00:04:45,660
Do you know who you are?

79
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:48,460
I certainly do.

80
00:04:49,380 --> 00:04:50,460
I just don't know

81
00:04:51,420 --> 00:04:53,220
how I annoyed you, Your Majesty.

82
00:04:56,100 --> 00:04:57,340
You're my woman.

83
00:04:57,940 --> 00:04:59,860
You have to always remember this.

84
00:05:04,740 --> 00:05:05,420
Yes.

85
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:07,660
I'll keep that in mind.

86
00:05:08,580 --> 00:05:09,420
In this case,

87
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:11,780
I'd like to see

88
00:05:12,860 --> 00:05:14,180
how you'll please me.

89
00:05:18,020 --> 00:05:19,060
I...

90
00:05:20,660 --> 00:05:21,940
I'll undress you, Your Majesty.

91
00:05:28,100 --> 00:05:32,380
♪Winter snow gently falls into the yard♪

92
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:37,820
♪There is no mercy in the palace♪

93
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:42,260
♪The further, the harder.
How brave do I have to be to reappear?♪

94
00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:42,940
Your Majesty.

95
00:05:44,940 --> 00:05:50,180
♪Is the murmuring memory
a dream or a fantasy?♪

96
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:54,300
♪Butterflies can fly
over the mountains for love♪

97
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:56,180
♪And die before the flowers♪

98
00:05:56,180 --> 00:05:57,540
You're my woman.

99
00:05:58,420 --> 00:06:00,260
Who are you keeping your integrity for?

100
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:02,500
Your Majesty, if you want my body.

101
00:06:03,580 --> 00:06:05,300
I can give it to you at any time.

102
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:07,340
But my heart

103
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:09,180
isn't yours.

104
00:06:09,180 --> 00:06:14,300
♪If you agree to meet me,
I'll have nothing to regret♪

105
00:06:14,620 --> 00:06:20,340
♪You're the unattainable star♪

106
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:26,140
♪I'm the tiniest dust in the world♪

107
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:26,740
Get out.

108
00:06:28,020 --> 00:06:29,300
Get out and kneel.

109
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:32,460
♪With love and hate,
we look into each other's eyes♪

110
00:06:34,220 --> 00:06:34,980
Yes.

111
00:06:34,980 --> 00:06:38,540
♪As the wind blows, the petals dance♪

112
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:44,460
♪You're the unattainable star♪

113
00:06:44,700 --> 00:06:50,420
♪I'm the tiniest dust in the world♪

114
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:54,260
♪With all the sincerity I can muster
for your kiss after the tears♪

115
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:56,540
Lady Ling has fallen out of favor
after only a few days.

116
00:06:56,980 --> 00:06:58,260
A slave is a slave.

117
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,140
His Majesty just wanted
to try something new.

118
00:07:00,300 --> 00:07:02,940
I heard her slave friend suffered, too.

119
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:04,340
Madam nearly beat her to death.

120
00:07:04,340 --> 00:07:05,100
Say no more.

121
00:07:05,100 --> 00:07:06,420
♪Butterflies can fly
over the mountains for love♪

122
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:08,940
♪And die before the flowers♪

123
00:07:09,380 --> 00:07:14,900
♪You're far away and you're right here♪

124
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:17,500
♪The game we play is destiny♪

125
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:20,780
♪I fancy myself by your side♪

126
00:07:20,940 --> 00:07:26,340
♪If you agree to meet me,
I'll have nothing to regret♪

127
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:28,980
♪You're the unattainable star♪

128
00:07:28,980 --> 00:07:29,780
Ask her to leave.

129
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:31,380
Get out of my face.

130
00:07:32,620 --> 00:07:38,100
♪I'm the tiniest dust in the world♪

131
00:07:38,100 --> 00:07:40,340
If you do this for me,

132
00:07:40,860 --> 00:07:43,300
I'll release you and your clansmen.

133
00:07:48,260 --> 00:07:50,540
I'm at your service,
Your Royal Highness.

134
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:55,780
Help!

135
00:07:56,220 --> 00:07:57,500
Please spare me.

136
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:00,900
Come over!

137
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:03,580
Madam, please spare me.

138
00:08:04,020 --> 00:08:04,620
Madam...

139
00:08:06,220 --> 00:08:06,860
Stop.

140
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:10,700
Lingzhi.

141
00:08:11,060 --> 00:08:11,580
Come back here.

142
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:14,460
Isn't this Lady Ling

143
00:08:14,620 --> 00:08:16,860
who got some favor and fell out of it?

144
00:08:20,180 --> 00:08:20,820
Madam,

145
00:08:21,620 --> 00:08:22,780
I don't want to give you a hard time.

146
00:08:24,100 --> 00:08:25,380
I'm taking Qingyan away.

147
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:27,060
From this day on,

148
00:08:27,820 --> 00:08:29,300
she belongs to Tinghan Palace.

149
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:32,380
Everything in the harem

150
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:35,500
is in the charge of Concubine Huan.

151
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:38,940
A Lady like you
have no authority to give orders.

152
00:08:39,780 --> 00:08:40,420
Not to mention

153
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:42,740
you're a Lady who fell from grace.

154
00:08:42,740 --> 00:08:43,340
How dare you!

155
00:08:44,180 --> 00:08:44,980
Don't forget

156
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:47,780
that I'm a Lady
while you're just a servant.

157
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:53,540
Lady An used to be glorious,

158
00:08:55,820 --> 00:08:58,540
but she ended up dead.

159
00:08:59,020 --> 00:09:01,340
Life in the harem is just this cruel!

160
00:09:01,420 --> 00:09:04,940
Without power, you can't save anyone!

161
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:12,780
She's right.

162
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:14,780
I have no power.

163
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:16,740
I can't save Qingyan.

164
00:09:17,260 --> 00:09:18,940
Nor can I save
my brother or other clansmen.

165
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:20,900
So, I must...

166
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:36,660
Your Majesty, I know I'm wrong.

167
00:09:37,340 --> 00:09:38,940
Could you please forgive me?

168
00:09:50,060 --> 00:09:53,100
Do you know what you have done wrong?

169
00:09:54,260 --> 00:09:55,380
I...

170
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,340
I shouldn't have disobeyed you,
Your Majesty.

171
00:10:00,700 --> 00:10:02,220
Is this how you apologize?

172
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:18,940
Your Majesty, as long as you forgive me,

173
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:21,580
I can do anything.

174
00:10:31,220 --> 00:10:32,900
You've ruined my mood for drinking wine.

175
00:10:33,940 --> 00:10:34,780
Get lost!

176
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:53,260
You evil Emperor,

177
00:10:53,260 --> 00:10:54,500
I'm going to kill you!

178
00:10:58,620 --> 00:11:00,180
Lingzhi, Lingzhi.

179
00:11:01,140 --> 00:11:01,740
Lingzhi!

180
00:11:10,220 --> 00:11:12,020
To regain your trust,

181
00:11:12,780 --> 00:11:14,660
I have to risk my life.

182
00:11:17,660 --> 00:11:19,540
♪Falling into a story♪

183
00:11:20,300 --> 00:11:23,460
♪I disturbed a dream♪

184
00:11:24,620 --> 00:11:26,700
♪I used to be a speck of dust♪

185
00:11:27,380 --> 00:11:30,260
♪Involved in delusion♪

186
00:11:31,940 --> 00:11:34,260
♪If the illusion of life♪

187
00:11:35,660 --> 00:11:37,460
♪Was sealed in time♪

188
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:40,380
♪I'd wake up from obsession♪

189
00:11:40,620 --> 00:11:43,180
♪And kiss you hard♪

190
00:11:45,860 --> 00:11:47,860
♪Grass always faded silently♪

191
00:11:48,540 --> 00:11:50,980
♪With no one knowing that♪

192
00:11:52,980 --> 00:11:54,940
♪The unavenged revenge♪

193
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:58,660
♪Rooted deeper♪

194
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:02,540
♪If love had never♪

195
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:05,700
♪Broken into my heart♪

196
00:12:06,140 --> 00:12:08,660
♪When I looked back, I'd miss♪

197
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:12,380
♪Who I met at first sight♪

198
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:16,180
♪I kept dreaming about you♪

199
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:19,460
♪But I had to sleep alone♪

200
00:12:19,740 --> 00:12:21,500
♪I'd forget♪

201
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:26,100
♪All the miserable old memories♪

202
00:12:26,820 --> 00:12:29,060
♪Expecting to get wet
in the snow when I'm old♪
